main event: A civilian reported seeing a UFO over Denver, Colorado on August 23, 1952 at around 11:00 PM.
interesting points: The UFO was observed for 25 minutes.
The UFO was moving southwest at a slow speed, too slow for a normal aircraft.
The report includes photographs of the UFO.
The report also includes physical evidence of the sighting.
The conclusion was that the sighting was probably an aircraft, but the duration of the sighting was too long for a normal aircraft.
